      %h2 ContentLength
      
      %p
        The ContentLength plugin is extremely small and simple, it's task is
        to assign the
        %em Content-Length
        header when not present. Keep in mind this is not possibly with
        streamed data, so if you are streaming a file, you should 
        %em stat()
        it and then assign
        %em Content-Length
        with
        %em stat.size
        before streaming.